data.description:
PRICE REDUCED ON THIS BENT TREE BLUFFS BEAUTY!  Stunning 2 story that has had everything updated with the latest finishes.  Beautiful entry with curving stair case & hardwood floors throughout 1st floor.  Great room has beamed ceiling & gas fireplace.  Kitchen has granite tops, painted cabinets, gas cooktop in island, stainless appliances and nice eating area.  Formal dining room off the entry.  Master BR is vaulted ceiling and fan into updated master bath with free standing tub and separate shower.  LVP flooring throughout bath.  Nice walk in closet and linen closet.  Bedrooms all have ceiling fans.  BR 4 has ship lap siding and sitting area in addition to nice bedroom space.  Hall bath has granite, tile and ship lap.  Lower level has a large finished family room with LVP flooring.  Great space for movies, games & family time.  Lots of storage area as well.  Exterior has stone trim and white and black finish.  Huge deck for entertaining.  Roof & gutter guards in September 2023. 
 Location is great and home looks like a model.  Very well cared for and move in ready.    Neighborhood amenities include pool, fishing ponds, and disc golf.  Don't miss out on this home in convenient location and nice neighborhood.
SELLER IS OFFERING $4,000 IN BUY DOWN RATE OR CLOSING COST CONCESSIONS!
